## Step 6: Persist Mobile Stack Config to CLAUDE.md

Add or update the `## Mobile Stack` section in `CLAUDE.md`:

```markdown
## Mobile Stack

- ecosystem: <detected>
- has_ios: <true|false>
- has_android: <true|false>
- test: <test command>
- build_ios: <ios build command or N/A>
- build_android: <android build command or N/A>
- analyze: <analyze command>
- bundle_id: <bundle_id>
- min_ios: <version or N/A>
- min_android: <api_level or N/A>
```

---

## Step 7: Initial Commit

Stage all scaffold files (explicitly — never `git add .`):

```bash
git init 2>/dev/null || true
git add CLAUDE.md .github/ src/ lib/ pubspec.yaml package.json \
        build.gradle.kts settings.gradle.kts \
        Package.swift app.json eas.json \
        .gitignore .env.development .env.staging .env.production 2>/dev/null || true
git commit -m "chore: scaffold <ecosystem> mobile project with CI/CD and testing"
```

